<st-panel app>
  <a-row :class="bstep()" class="mg-b48 mg-t48" :gutter="8">
    <a-col offset="1" :span="stepsSpan">
      <a-steps :current="currentIndex">
        <a-step
          v-for="item in stepArr"
          :key="item.key"
          :title="item.title"
          class="cursor-pointer"
        />
      </a-steps>
    </a-col>
  </a-row>
  <staff-detail-basics
    v-if="currentIndex == 0"
    :codeList="codeList"
    :roleList="roleList"
    @addStep="addCoachInfo"
    @deletStep="deletStep"
  />
</st-panel>
